# Bulky, reproducible raw artifacts — distilled forms are committed:
#   results.json (.aggregate + .self_test), paired_ab.json (per-run wall_tps/e_accept/clocks),
#   full.log (orchestrator attestation + verdict), attestation.txt (server-log evidence excerpt).
# Raw decode token dumps and verbose vLLM server logs (~23MB) are not committed.
**/decode/*.jsonl
**/server_run*.log
